=head1 NAME

_INSTRUMENT_HELLO_ -- Performs the INGRID-specific imaging setup.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive is performs the instrument specific setup for
imaging.  It's needed for the generic L<_IMAGING_HELLO_|_IMAGING_HELLO_>.
In this case it merely reports that the set-up operations are
complete.

=head1 NOTES

=over 4

=item *

This primitive is suitable for INGRID.

=back

